.DT
shuffle_new_leader
Disk World creator help
shuffle_new_leader

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
shuffle_new_leader -  This function allows you to choose a new leader for the group in a variety of ways.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs object shuffle_new_leader(string group,
int way,
object * exclude)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^group%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^way%^RESET%^ - 0 for random (no other ways present atm)
%^BOLD%^exclude%^RESET%^ - an object array of members to exclude from the start
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
an object pointing to the new leader, or 0
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function allows you to choose a new leader for the group
in a variety of ways.  It only includes players who are
interactive().

.EP

